  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Clan</p><p>Prerequisite: Chinoike Clan, Level 8+</p><p>Your Ketsuryūgan improves in efficiency and speed due to your dedication to your clan's bloodwork. You gain the following benefits;</p><p>• Increase your Intelligence or Wisdom score by +1, to a maximum of 20</p><p>• While your Ketsuryūgan is active, you cannot be Dazzled or Concussed.</p><p>• You now regain half your expanded uses of your Ketsuryūgan features on a short rest.</p><p>• Once per full rest, you may use a corpse of medium size or larger to regain uses of your Ketsuryūgan as if you took a short rest. If you have the Sanguine Adept feat, you can do this with any sized corpse</p>",
